        {
            "title": "高盛預計銅價突破11000美元的創紀錄漲勢恐難持久",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 高盛給銅價前景潑了一些冷水。這家華爾街大行認為，銅價突破每噸11,000美元的漲勢恐難持久，因為目前全球銅供應仍足以滿足需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛分析師在報告中寫道：「近期銅價漲勢主要基於對未來市場供應趨緊的預期，而非當前基本面。我們預計此次突破11,000美元的漲勢不會持久。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">倫敦期銅周三創下每噸11,540美元的紀錄新高，倫敦金屬交易所(LME)倉庫銅提貨申請量激增加劇了美國關稅風險引發的供應擔憂。貿易商摩科瑞上周警告美國以外地區的銅市場供應極易受到低庫存的影響。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cdef06de-3fa5-3c63-aee0-847ea9392233-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然高盛上調了對於明年上半年銅價的預測，並表示美國關稅驅動的銅供應風險將支撐價格，但該行指出，通過更高的區域升水和更緊的LME價差，可以避免美國以外地區出現「極低」庫存。高盛預計，今年的需求將比供應少約50萬噸，直到2029年全球銅市場都不會出現供應短缺。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛分析師指出：「儘管我們預計2026年銅供應將比需求僅多出約16萬噸，使市場更趨平衡，但這意味著我們認為全球銅市場短期內不會出現供應短缺。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新加坡時間周四中午12點，LME期銅上漲0.23%，報每噸11513.5美元，今年以來漲幅擴大至31%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Says Copper’s ‘Breakout’ Above $11,000 Won’t Last</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E9%8A%85%E5%83%B9%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B411000%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E7%9A%84%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%BC%B2%E5%8B%A2%E6%81%90%E9%9B%A3%E6%8C%81%E4%B9%85-041241106.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 13:00:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
